(17,	17,	'Latte helper to protect your email address',	'# Latte email helper\n\nSmall Latte helper based on Smarty idea to protect your email address.\n\n-----\n\n[![Build Status](https://img.shields.io/travis/minetro/latte-email.svg?style=flat-square)](https://travis-ci.org/minetro/latte-email)\n[![Downloads total](https://img.shields.io/packagist/dt/minetro/latte-email.svg?style=flat-square)](https://packagist.org/packages/minetro/latte-email)\n[![Latest stable](https://img.shields.io/packagist/v/minetro/latte-email.svg?style=flat-square)](https://packagist.org/packages/minetro/latte-email)\n[![HHVM Status](https://img.shields.io/hhvm/minetro/latte-email.svg?style=flat-square)](http://hhvm.h4cc.de/package/minetro/latte-email)\n\n## Discussion / Help\n\n[![Join the chat at https://gitter.im/Markette/Gopay](https://img.shields.io/gitter/room/minetro/nette.svg?style=flat-square)](https://gitter.im/minetro/nette?utm_source=badge&utm_medium=badge&utm_campaign=pr-badge&utm_content=badge)\n\n## Install\n\n```sh\ncomposer require minetro/latte-email:~1.2.0\n```\n\n## Usage\n\nRegister in **TemplateFactory** or in `createTemplate()` or in your **config.neon**.\n\n```php\nuse Minetro\\Latte\\Helpers\\EmailHelper;\n\nEmailHelper::mailto($email, $encode = NULL, $text = NULL)\n```\n\n### List of encoding\n* javascript\n* javascript_charcode\n* hex\n* drupal\n* texy\n\n## Latte syntax\n\n```\n{var $mail = \"my@email.net\"}\n\n{$mail|email:\"javascript\"}\n{$mail|email:\"javascript_charcode\"}\n{$mail|email:\"hex\"|noescape}\n{$mail|email:\"javascript\":\"link to my email here\"}\n{$mail|email:\"drupal\"}\n{$mail|email:\"texy\"}\n```\n',	'<div class=\"announce instapaper_body md\" data-path=\"README.md\" id=\"readme\"><article class=\"markdown-body entry-content\" itemprop=\"text\"><h1><a id=\"user-content-latte-email-helper\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"https://github.com/minetro/latte-email/#latte-email-helper\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path d=\"M4 9h1v1h-1c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5s1.55-3.5 3-3.5h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-0.91 2.72-2 3.25v-1.16c0.58-0.45 1-1.27 1-2.09 0-1.28-1.02-2.5-2-2.5H4c-0.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5s1 2.5 2 2.5z m9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5s-1.02 2.5-2 2.5H9c-0.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-0.83 0.42-1.64 1-2.09v-1.16c-1.09 0.53-2 1.84-2 3.25 0 1.81 1.55 3.5 3 3.5h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5s-1.5-3.5-3-3.5z\"></path></svg></a>Latte email helper</h1>\n\n<p>Small Latte helper based on Smarty idea to protect your email address.</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://travis-ci.org/minetro/latte-email\"><img href=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/571b03b520632662215fa379bde04abb3b4bf9db/68747470733a2f2f696d672e736869656c64732e696f2f7472617669732f6d696e6574726f2f6c617474652d656d61696c2e7376673f7374796c653d666c61742d737175617265\" alt=\"Build Status\" data-canonical-href=\"https://img.shields.io/travis/minetro/latte-email.svg?style=flat-square\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://packagist.org/packages/minetro/latte-email\"><img href=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/c0a898fa29a9091b4bd0f7c7d8449e527160162e/68747470733a2f2f696d672e736869656c64732e696f2f7061636b61676973742f64742f6d696e6574726f2f6c617474652d656d61696c2e7376673f7374796c653d666c61742d737175617265\" alt=\"Downloads total\" data-canonical-href=\"https://img.shields.io/packagist/dt/minetro/latte-email.svg?style=flat-square\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://packagist.org/packages/minetro/latte-email\"><img href=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/623434fdbc90c6afd4530011980fada9719fcac5/68747470733a2f2f696d672e736869656c64732e696f2f7061636b61676973742f762f6d696e6574726f2f6c617474652d656d61696c2e7376673f7374796c653d666c61742d737175617265\" alt=\"Latest stable\" data-canonical-href=\"https://img.shields.io/packagist/v/minetro/latte-email.svg?style=flat-square\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"http://hhvm.h4cc.de/package/minetro/latte-email\"><img href=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/751fe4a3871f5afe5aaa92348c502305a3ae9e80/68747470733a2f2f696d672e736869656c64732e696f2f6868766d2f6d696e6574726f2f6c617474652d656d61696c2e7376673f7374796c653d666c61742d737175617265\" alt=\"HHVM Status\" data-canonical-href=\"https://img.shields.io/hhvm/minetro/latte-email.svg?style=flat-square\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n\n<h2><a id=\"user-content-discussion--help\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"https://github.com/minetro/latte-email/#discussion--help\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path d=\"M4 9h1v1h-1c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5s1.55-3.5 3-3.5h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-0.91 2.72-2 3.25v-1.16c0.58-0.45 1-1.27 1-2.09 0-1.28-1.02-2.5-2-2.5H4c-0.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5s1 2.5 2 2.5z m9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5s-1.02 2.5-2 2.5H9c-0.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-0.83 0.42-1.64 1-2.09v-1.16c-1.09 0.53-2 1.84-2 3.25 0 1.81 1.55 3.5 3 3.5h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5s-1.5-3.5-3-3.5z\"></path></svg></a>Discussion / Help</h2>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://gitter.im/minetro/nette?utm_source=badge&amp;utm_medium=badge&amp;utm_campaign=pr-badge&amp;utm_content=badge\"><img href=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/10fe3cfb9b917911d1eb9d22432ce274abd40bdf/68747470733a2f2f696d672e736869656c64732e696f2f6769747465722f726f6f6d2f6d696e6574726f2f6e657474652e7376673f7374796c653d666c61742d737175617265\" alt=\"Join the chat at https://gitter.im/Markette/Gopay\" data-canonical-href=\"https://img.shields.io/gitter/room/minetro/nette.svg?style=flat-square\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n\n<h2><a id=\"user-content-install\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"https://github.com/minetro/latte-email/#install\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path d=\"M4 9h1v1h-1c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5s1.55-3.5 3-3.5h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-0.91 2.72-2 3.25v-1.16c0.58-