2-1.64 1-2.09v-1.16c-1.09 0.53-2 1.84-2 3.25 0 1.81 1.55 3.5 3 3.5h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5s-1.5-3.5-3-3.5z\"></path></svg></a>Discussion / Help</h2>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://gitter.im/minetro/nette?utm_source=badge&amp;utm_medium=badge&amp;utm_campaign=pr-badge&amp;utm_content=badge\"><img href=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/10fe3cfb9b917911d1eb9d22432ce274abd40bdf/68747470733a2f2f696d672e736869656c64732e696f2f6769747465722f726f6f6d2f6d696e6574726f2f6e657474652e7376673f7374796c653d666c61742d737175617265\" alt=\"Join the chat at https://gitter.im/Markette/Gopay\" data-canonical-href=\"https://img.shields.io/gitter/room/minetro/nette.svg?style=flat-square\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n\n<h2><a id=\"user-content-install\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"https://github.com/minetro/ntdb/#install\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path d=\"M4 9h1v1h-1c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5s1.55-3.5 3-3.5h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-0.91 2.72-2 3.25v-1.16c0.58-0.45 1-1.27 1-2.09 0-1.28-1.02-2.5-2-2.5H4c-0.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5s1 2.5 2 2.5z m9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5s-1.02 2.5-2 2.5H9c-0.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-0.83 0.42-1.64 1-2.09v-1.16c-1.09 0.53-2 1.84-2 3.25 0 1.81 1.55 3.5 3 3.5h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5s-1.5-3.5-3-3.5z\"></path></svg></a>Install</h2>\n\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-shell\"><pre>$ composer require minetro/ntdb</pre></div>\n\n<h2><a id=\"user-content-resources\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"https://github.com/minetro/ntdb/#resources\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path d=\"M4 9h1v1h-1c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5s1.55-3.5 3-3.5h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-0.91 2.72-2 3.25v-1.16c0.58-0.45 1-1.27 1-2.09 0-1.28-1.02-2.5-2-2.5H4c-0.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5s1 2.5 2 2.5z m9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5s-1.02 2.5-2 2.5H9c-0.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-0.83 0.42-1.64 1-2.09v-1.16c-1.09 0.53-2 1.84-2 3.25 0 1.81 1.55 3.5 3 3.5h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5s-1.5-3.5-3-3.5z\"></path></svg></a>Resources</h2>\n\n<p>Inspired by these articles:</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.yiiframework.com/wiki/38/how-to-use-nested-db-transactions-mysql-5-postgresql/\">http://www.yiiframework.com/wiki/38/how-to-use-nested-db-transactions-mysql-5-postgresql/</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.kennynet.co.uk/2008/12/02/php-pdo-nested-transactions/\">http://www.kennynet.co.uk/2008/12/02/php-pdo-nested-transactions/</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://gist.github.com/neoascetic/5269127\">https://gist.github.com/neoascetic/5269127</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2><a id=\"user-content-usage\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"https://github.com/minetro/ntdb/#usage\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path d=\"M4 9h1v1h-1c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5s1.55-3.5 3-3.5h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-0.91 2.72-2 3.25v-1.16c0.58-0.45 1-1.27 1-2.09 0-1.28-1.02-2.5-2-2.5H4c-0.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5s1 2.5 2 2.5z m9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5s-1.02 2.5-2 2.5H9c-0.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-0.83 0.42-1.64 1-2.09v-1.16c-1.09 0.53-2 1.84-2 3.25 0 1.81 1.55 3.5 3 3.5h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5s-1.5-3.5-3-3.5z\"></path></svg></a>Usage</h2>\n\n<p>Provide nested transaction via savepoints.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Support</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>MySQL / MySQLi</li>\n<li>PostgreSQL</li>\n<li>SQLite</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>API</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li><code>$t-&gt;begin</code></li>\n<li><code>$t-&gt;commit</code></li>\n<li><code>$t-&gt;rollback</code></li>\n<li><strong><code>$t-&gt;transaction</code></strong> or <strong><code>$t-&gt;t</code></strong></li>\n<li><code>$t-&gt;promise</code></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3><a id=\"user-content-begin\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"https://github.com/minetro/ntdb/#begin\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path d=\"M4 9h1v1h-1c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5s1.55-3.5 3-3.5h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-0.91 2.72-2 3.25v-1.16c0.58-0.45 1-1.27 1-2.09 0-1.28-1.02-2.5-2-2.5H4c-0.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5s1 2.5 2 2.5z m9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5s-1.02 2.5-2 2.5H9c-0.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-0.83 0.42-1.64 1-2.09v-1.16c-1.09 0.53-2 1.84-2 3.25 0 1.81 1.55 3.5 3 3.5h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5s-1.5-3.5-3-3.5z\"></path></svg></a>Begin</h3>\n\n<p>Starts transaction.</p>\n\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-text-html-php\"><pre><span class=\"pl-s1\"><span class=\"pl-smi\">$t</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">new</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">Transaction</span>(<span class=\"pl-k\">new</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">Connection</span>(<span class=\"pl-k\">...</span>));</span>\n<span class=\"pl-s1\"><span class=\"pl-smi\">$t</span><span class=\"pl-k\">-&gt;</span>begin();</span></pre></div>\n\n<h3><a id=\"user-content-commit\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"https://github.com/minetro/ntdb/#commit\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path d=\"M4 9h1v1h-1c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5s1.55-3.5 3-3.5h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-0.91 2.72-2 3.25v-1.16c0.58-0.45 1-1.27 1-2.09 0-1.28-1.02-2.5-2-2.5H4c-0.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5s1 2.5 2 2.5z m9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5s-1.02 2.5-2 2.5H9c-0.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-0.83 0.42-1.64 1-2.09v-1.16c-1.09 0.53-2 1.84-2 3.25 0 1.81 1.55 3.5 3 3.5h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5s-1.5-3.5-3-3.5z\"></path></svg></a>Commit</h3>\n\n<p>Commit changes in transaction.</p>\n\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-text-html-php\"><pre><span class=\"pl-s1\"><span class=\"pl-smi\">$t</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">new</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">Transaction</span>(<span class=\"pl-k\">new</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">Connection</span>(<span class=\"pl-k\">...</span>));</span>\n<span class=\"pl-s1\"><span class=\"pl-smi\">$t</span><span class=\"pl-k\">-&gt;</span>begin();</span>\n<span class=\"pl-s1\"><span class=\"pl-c\">// some changes..</span></span>\n<span class=\"pl-s1\"><span class=\"pl-smi\">$t</span><span class=\"pl-k\">-&gt;</span>commit();</span></pre></div>\n\n<h3><a id=\"user-content-rollback\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"https://github.com/minetro/ntdb/#rollback\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path d=\"M4 9h1v1h-1c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5s1.55-3.5 3-3.5h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-0.91 2.72-2 3.25v-1.16c0.58-0.45 1-1.27 1-2.09 0-1.28-1.02-2.5-2-2.5H4c-0.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5s1 2.5 2 2.5z m9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5s-1.02 2.5-2 2.5H9c-0.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-0.83 0.42-1.64 1-2.09v-1.16c-1.09 0.53-2 1.84-2 3.25 0 1.81 1.55 3.5 3 3.5h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5s-1.5-3.5-3-3.5z\"></path></svg></a>Rollback</h3>\n\n<p>Revert changes in transaction.</p>\n\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-text-html-php\"><pre><span class=\"pl-s1\"><span class=\"pl-smi\">$t</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">new</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">Transaction</span>(<span class=\"pl-k\">new</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">Connection</span>(<span class=\"pl-k\">...</span>));</span>\n<span class=\"pl-s1\"></span>\n<span class=\"pl-s1\"><span class=\"pl-smi\">$t</span><span class=\"pl-k\">-&gt;</span>begin();</span>\n<span class=\"pl-s1\"><span class=\"pl-k\">try</span> {</span>\n<span class=\"pl-s1\">    <span class=\"pl-c\">// some changes..</span></span>\n<span class=\"pl-s1\">    <span class=\"pl-smi\">$t</span><span class=\"pl-k\">-&gt;</span>commit();</span>\n<span class=\"pl-s1\">} <span class=\"pl-k\">catch</span> (<span class=\"pl-c1\">Exception</span> <span class=\"pl-smi\">$e</span>) {</span>\n<span class=\"pl-s1\">    <span class=\"pl-smi\">$t</span><span class=\"pl-k\">-&gt;</span>rollback();</span>\n<span class=\"pl-s1\">}</span></pre></div>\n\n<h3><a id=\"user-content-transaction\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"https://github.com/minetro/ntdb/#transaction\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path d=\"M4 9h1v1h-1c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5s1.55-3.5 3-3.5h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-0.91 2.72-2 3.25v-1.16c0.58-0.45 1-1.27 1-2.09 0-1.28-1.02-2.5-2-2.5H4c-0.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5s1 2.5 2 2.5z m9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5s-1.02 2.5-2 2.5H9c-0.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-0.83 0.42-1.64 1-2.09v-1.16c-1.09 0.53-2 1.84-2 3.25 0 1.81 1.55 3.5 3 3.5h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5s-1.5-3.5-3-3.5z\"></path></svg></a>Transaction</h3>\n\n<p>Combine begin, commit and rollback to one method.</p>\n\n<p>On success it commits changes, if exceptions is thrown it rollbacks changes.</p>\n\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-text-html-php\"><pre><span class=\"pl-s1\"><span class=\"pl-smi\">$t</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">new</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">Transaction</span>(<span class=\"pl-k\">new</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">Connection</span>(<span class=\"pl-k\">...</span>));</span>\n<span class=\"pl-s1\"></span>\n<span class=\"pl-s1\"><span class=\"pl-smi\">$t</span><span class=\"pl-k\">-&gt;</span>transaction(<span class=\"pl-k\">function</span>() {</span>\n<span class=\"pl-s1\">    <span class=\"pl-c\">// some changes..</span></span>\n<span class=\"pl-s1\">});</span>\n<span class=\"pl-s1\"></span>\n<span class=\"pl-s1\"><span class=\"pl-c\">// or alias</span></span>\n<span class=\"pl-s1\"></span>\n<span class=\"pl-s1\"><span class=\"pl-smi\">$t</span><span class=\"pl-k\">-&gt;</span>t(<span class=\"pl-k\">function</span>() {</span>\n<span class=\"pl-s1\">    <span class=\"pl-c\">// some changes..</span></span>\n<span class=\"pl-s1\">});</span></pre></div>\n\n<h3><a id=\"user-content-promise\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"https://github.com/minetro/ntdb/#promise\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path d=\"M4 9h1v1h-1c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5s1.55-3.5 3-3.5h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-0.91 2.72-2 3.25v-1.16c0.58-0.45 1-1.27 1-2.09 0-1.28-1.02-2.5-2-2.5H4c-0.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5s1 2.5 2 2.5z m9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5s-1.02 2.5-2 2.5H9c-0.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-0.83 0.42-1.64 1-2.09v-1.16c-1.09 0.53-2 1.84-2 3.25 0 1.81 1.55 3.5 3 3.5h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5s-1.5-3.5-3-3.5z\"></path></svg></a>Promise</h3>\n\n<p>Another attitude to transaction.</p>\n\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-text-html-php\"><pre><span class=\"pl-s1\"><span class=\"pl-smi\">$t</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">new</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">Transaction</span>(<span class=\"pl-k\">new</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">Connection</span>(<span class=\"pl-k\">...</span>));</span>\n<span class=\"pl-s1\"></span>\n<span class=\"pl-s1\"><span class=\"pl-smi\">$t</span><span class=\"pl-k\">-&gt;</span>promise()<span class=\"pl-k\">-&gt;</span>then(</span>\n<span class=\"pl-s1\">    <span class=\"pl-k\">function</span>() {</span>\n<span class=\"pl-s1\">        <span class=\"pl-c\">// Logic.. (save/update/remove some data)</span></span>\n<span class=\"pl-s1\">    }, </span>\n<span class=\"pl-s1\">    <span class=\"pl-k\">function</span> () {</span>\n<span class=\"pl-s1\">        <span class=\"pl-c\">// Success.. (after commit)</span></span>\n<span class=\"pl-s1\">    },</span>\n<span class=\"pl-s1\">    <span class=\"pl-k\">function</span>() {</span>\n<span class=\"pl-s1\">        <span class=\"pl-c\">// Failed.. (after rollback)</span></span>\n<span class=\"pl-s1\">    }      </span>\n<span class=\"pl-s1\">);</span></pre></div>\n\n<h3><a id=\"user-content-unresolvedtransactionexception\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"https://github.com/minetro/ntdb/#unresolvedtransactionexception\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path d=\"M4 9h1v1h-1c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5s1.55-3.5 3-3.5h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 