2 2.5H9c-0.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-0.83 0.42-1.64 1-2.09v-1.16c-1.09 0.53-2 1.84-2 3.25 0 1.81 1.55 3.5 3 3.5h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5s-1.5-3.5-3-3.5z\"></path></svg></a>Extension</h2>\n\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-yaml\"><pre><span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-ent\">extensions:</span></span>\n    <span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-ent\">captcha:</span> <span class=\"pl-s\">Minetro\\SeznamCaptcha\\DI\\SeznamCaptchaExtension</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-ent\">captcha:</span></span>\n    <span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-ent\">auto:</span> <span class=\"pl-s\">on / off</span></span></pre></div>\n\n<h2><a id=\"user-content-usage\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"https://github.com/minetro/seznamcaptcha/#usage\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path d=\"M4 9h1v1h-1c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5s1.55-3.5 3-3.5h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-0.91 2.72-2 3.25v-1.16c0.58-0.45 1-1.27 1-2.09 0-1.28-1.02-2.5-2-2.5H4c-0.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5s1 2.5 2 2.5z m9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5s-1.02 2.5-2 2.5H9c-0.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-0.83 0.42-1.64 1-2.09v-1.16c-1.09 0.53-2 1.84-2 3.25 0 1.81 1.55 3.5 3 3.5h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5s-1.5-3.5-3-3.5z\"></path></svg></a>Usage</h2>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/minetro/seznamcaptcha/master/captcha.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/minetro/seznamcaptcha/master/captcha.png\" alt=\"captcha\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n\n<h3><a id=\"user-content-automatic\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"https://github.com/minetro/seznamcaptcha/#automatic\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path d=\"M4 9h1v1h-1c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5s1.55-3.5 3-3.5h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-0.91 2.72-2 3.25v-1.16c0.58-0.45 1-1.27 1-2.09 0-1.28-1.02-2.5-2-2.5H4c-0.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5s1 2.5 2 2.5